Authorization: Bearer xxx

##------------> MENUS

### Get all Menus
GET http://localhost:1337/api/Menus
  ?populate=* HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer xxx

### Get all Menus for a specific day
GET http://localhost:1337/api/Menus
  ?filters[Date][$eq]=2025-02-15 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer xxx

### Get all Menus for a specific day with relations
GET http://localhost:1337/api/menus
  ?filters[Date][$eq]=2025-02-15&populate[breakfast][fields][0]=documentId
  &populate[lunch][fields][0]=documentId
  &populate[supper][fields][0]=documentId&populate[resident][fields][0]=full_name HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer xxx

### Get all Menus for a specific resident
GET http://localhost:1337/api/Menus
  ?filters[resident][slug][$contains]=helen-serpa HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer xxx

### POST A NEW MENU
POST http://localhost:1337/api/Menus HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer xxx

